short.ar: في لعبة الشيف هذه ، عليك استخدام جميع مهاراتك في الطهي أثناء صنع السباغيتي.
short.am: በዚህ የወጥ ቤት ጨዋታ ውስጥ ስፓጌቲ በምትሰራበት ጊዜ የወጥ ቤት ሥራ የማብሰል ችሎታህን በሙሉ መጠቀም አለብህ።

short.en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,lt,pt_BR,pt_: In this chef game, you have to use all your cooking chef skills while making spaghetti.
short.es: En este juego de chef, tienes que usar todas tus habilidades de chef de cocina mientras haces espaguetis.

short.he: במשחק השף הזה, אתה צריך להשתמש בכל כישורי שף הבישול שלך תוך כדי הכנת ספגטי.

short.ko: 이 요리사 게임에서는 스파게티를 만드는 동안 모든 요리 요리사 기술을 사용해야합니다.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you like to make pasta! Make your longest pasta and show your cooking skills with a fun adventure game.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Spaghetti Chef Game Features
✓ 4 Different Mode
✓ Colorful Graphics
✓ Easy control
✓ Infinity Level

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Spaghetti Chef Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
